name: CottonCandy Pastel
description:
Prepare to showcase your colorful images!

CottonCandy Pastel prioritizes the creation of colorful, vibrant, and visually captivating images.

Recommended prompts: (colorful, vivid color:1.4)

*The model has already been baked with the Pastel-Mix VAE. If you use AUTOMATIC1111, you can set the VAE to None in the settings to use the built-in VAE. However, I have just finished uploading a separate VAE.

- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
If you find value in this model and want to help take it to new heights, you can support towards upgrading my GPU on Ko-fi or Buy Me a Coffee

If there's anything you need, please don't hesitate to let me know.

- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
Here are my other models:

CalicoMix a general-purpose model.

CalicoMixReal a realistic version of CalicoMix.

CalicoMix DC a simplified variant with a cuter appeal.
